{"tid":1985860,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"走失貓","createTime":"2020-04-23T12:29:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-01T08:31:34.000Z","uid":251920,"like":4,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"1ef0ca1ef044781026204977fd3976c4331ebdf1","tid":1985860,"uid":251920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T12:29:54.000Z","msg":"今日4月23號我屋企隻貓走失左<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MpvYB3u.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMpvYB3u.jpg&h=b8ce3c3d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nRjiB5Z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnRjiB5Z.jpg&h=a8dd7d91&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XadfEjp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXadfEjp.jpg&h=1c323fea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我住係佐敦，九龍祐寧堂隔離<br />\n雙親話佢地今日下晝1600-1800出左街，但無為意佢地出街時隻貓有無跟住衝左出去<br />\n我住啲單幢大廈，每層都有防煙門<br />\n屋企裝哂窗紗，所以都幾肯定佢無跳窗<br />\n宜家係擔心佢真係咁啱過到防煙門，因為直通天台，咁我就覺得兇多吉少<br />\n如果住附近麻煩幫手望望<br />\n唔該哂 :("},{"pid":"e823cfd06d4b8bf964a71a44e4fddb5ade3d6c8f","tid":1985860,"uid":258578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T12:31:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c5a9ec3ef1fb29ddf193e68f12c401e0f3eafe52","tid":1985860,"uid":106544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T12:36:41.000Z","msg":"貼街招啦"},{"pid":"606a638cd601dff9b2943ea9fa1c9c53012f5f4d","tid":1985860,"uid":3987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T12:37:19.000Z","msg":"一年就走失 仲有十幾年點捱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9fb97c89e6979d03c1c075f74a6308faefbf48d","tid":1985860,"uid":190847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T12:40:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48adaf23f820da33473de86f9e3af1e3abd558e6","tid":1985860,"uid":344625,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"